  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "add the garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "add the cherry tomatoes and cook for 2-3 minutes, until they start to release their juices.",
    "stir in the parsley, feta cheese, lemon juice, red wine vinegar, salt, and black pepper.",
    "add the cooked linguine pasta to the skillet and toss everything together.",
    "top with grated parmesan cheese and kalamata olives.",
    "serve immediately and enjoy!",
    "consider serving with a side of garlic bread or a green salad for a more filling meal."
